name: Club Jenna Presents: Jenna Jameson's Strip Poker
overview: Club Jenna Presents: Jenna Jameson's Strip Poker is a strip poker simulation starring 90's and early 2000s adult film star Jenna Jameson. It was developed and manufactured by Shiggles, Inc. However, the year of release is currently unknown. It was, however, released sometime in the early-mid 2000s.
